{"tid":1471584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急]要攻破輿論戰 必須攻其弱點","createTime":"2019-08-14T10:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T10:22:18.000Z","uid":225916,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"26a132a359312433d78c70e77f1b5ecec4f617ce","tid":1471584,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:02:32.000Z","msg":"政府正不斷進行緊政治抹黑<br />\n不斷放鬼，一來分化及擾亂，更重要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">散播示威者暴力、擾民嘅形象</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我哋要針對政府哩點做文宣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">指責政府一直抹黑示威者</span><br />\n<br />\n行為包括:<br />\n1.將警察卧底放入示威者之中，做出極端暴力行為，<span style=\"color: red;\">企圖將示威者形象抹黑</span>，包括丟汽油彈、磚頭、利用丫叉彈鋼珠。卧底更混入示威者之中，故意制造衝突及暴力，試圖令警察武力升級合理化。<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: red;\">利用媒體抹黑示威者</span>，TVB新聞報導失實，將示威片段刪減以及斷章取義，將示威者行為妖魔化。<br />\n<br />\n3.政府進行洗腦式記者招待會，<span style=\"color: red;\">將經濟及民生問題歸咎示威者</span>，而並不承認現時政府管治無能。政府應深刻反思，何以香港社會會步入現時困局，歸根究底就是政府漠視民意，將社會撕裂。<br />\n<br />\n4.8月13日機管局表示下許航班全數取消，但與事實不符，故意令旅客和示威者造成混亂，令原以為航班取消，然後變為錯過航班，引起旅客和示威者發生衝突，然後再<span style=\"color: red;\">以示威者阻止遊客上機之名進行抹黑</span>。<br />\n<br />\n5.將疑似公安人士投放入示威者之中，再利用警員卧底，假裝揭發其身份，再煽動示威者情緒以及造出暴力行為。最後將可疑人士說成旅客，企圖造成:示威者襲擊旅客形象，目的是分化示威者、抹黑示威者形象、將暴力執法合理化、以及申請法庭禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n6.中央電視台制造假新聞，自編自演汽油彈事件。不知從何而來的受燒傷警員，以假新聞作為證據抹黑示威者，可惜最終被揭穿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上種種事實可證明政府抹黑我哋<br />\n日後會使出更多無恥招數，更有可能故意造成人命傷亡去抹黑示威者，希望各位多加小心，宣揚政府惡行"},{"pid":"105d2fe76cab81a241aba423bdcc995cd6fa08a5","tid":1471584,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  &amp; 借位 post<br />\n<br />\n（尋失物) 今日13/8 喺機場唔見咗個背囊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n緊急 8月5號 深水埗 有冇手足執到？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"14fed4e88bd6c762f094b849f6d97a2f729856d2","tid":1471584,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:05:54.000Z","msg":"我好少可打咁大段嘢 希望文宣可以以此方向進行<br />\n攻破輿論戰，一切行為都係政府派人去做<br />\n當然 811 721必不可小<br />\n全力攻其弱點"},{"pid":"e0356e02f4bb025532010d49010f33dcba9a41ba","tid":1471584,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:07:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"191f3b728342444f36f8f3a6c55f8753a58bd4cb","tid":1471584,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http